Here’s a little something @stevecarlson and I cooked up while writing in the mountains.  The full @radiocomusic volume 2 gets released next month.  Hope y’all enjoy. 😎

Sometimes you just gotta get out there and make it happen.

node.text: Here is the panel discussion that took place on Saturday.  If you missed it...have a listen.  If you caught it...listen again.  If we don’t stop and listen...we can never truly see.  People are hurting.  People are in pain.  Indifference is ignorance.  Education is everywhere.  Listen and learn.  Or ignore, stay silent and perpetuate the pain of others.  Thank you to @realdaryldavis @brionajenkins @baratunde & @rev_deborah_johnson for your words and insight, your work and your inspiration.  I pledge to arm myself and my family with wisdom and empathy.  And to stand strong in support of communities of color.  #blacklivesmatter

node.text: Okay @stephenamell , @grantgust and all you other Supes out there...I’m beginning to understand the struggle. 😥. Or maybe I’m just too old for this crap.  @theboystv @amazonprimevideo #soldierboy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jensen Ackles on May 30, 2021 tagging @danneelackles512. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and snow.

node.text:
Today is my little girl’s 8th birthday. And the first one I’ve ever missed. Oh, how I wish I could be with her. It breaks my heart that I’m not. And it breaks my heart to see her growing so fast. I wish I could slow time for us. I truly do. But those are super powers I haven’t quite figured out just yet. If anyone has a hack for that...please let me know. 

-Me aka JJ’s Dad
(Operating virtually)
